item.title: Happy Birthday, Gracelyn
item.dc:creator: troyh
item.content:encoded: We packed the kids in the car right after their midday naps and went to Newcastle, WA to Julie and Hans' house for Gracelyn's 1st birthday party. On the way home I resisted the Fry's in Renton and we went to get takeout at Buddha Ruksa in West Seattle. I'm not sure why we did because we weren't very hungry after eating at the party, but we ate a little of it when we got home and left most of it for dinner tomorrow night.
